##DATA SCIENCE!!!
It is the future!!

With all the experiences I had with Data as a Database programmer, I am all fascinated about dealing with data. Thinking on What I can do more on data let me land in a profession as a data scientist.

My recent studies on Machine Learning concepts with R Programming helped me achieve my career goal to become a data scientist who can do data analysis, wrangling, modelling and solving the data problems.

## Checkout
Visit my GitHub repositories at  @prsshini to view my various projects and Machine Learning tasks.

* [Kaggle Experience on Whats Cooking Data](http://prsshini.github.io/Kaggle_WhatsCooking )

* [Machine Learning Tasks](http://prsshini.github.io/Machine-Learning-Algorithms/)
